title: Death Note Series [English Dubbed]
description:
----------------
Death Note
----------------
This series centers around a high school student named Light who discovers a supernatural notebook that allows him to kill anyone by writing the victim's name and picturing his or her face. The plot follows his attempt to create and lead a world cleansed of evil using the book, and the complex conflict between himself and those assailing him that results.

This is the entire series, all 37 episodes. They are TV Rip so it is not quite DVD quality but very much watchable.

If you download this PLEASE SEED!


Enjoy this great show!
